<%= render "partials/header" %>

<header class="bg-dark py-5">
    <div class="container px-5">
        <div class="row gx-5 align-items-center justify-content-center">

            <div class="col-lg-8 col-xl-7 col-xxl-6">
                <div class="my-5 text-center text-xl-start">
                    <h1 class="display-5 fw-bolder text-white mb-3">Welcome to ICCOBA UK/Europe</h1>
                    <p class="lead fw-normal text-white-50 mb-4">12th–14th September 2025 Convention
                    <p class="lead fw-normal text-white-50 mb-4">Theme: “Brothers Beyond Borders: Honouring the Legacy”</p>
                    <p class="lead fw-normal text-white-50 mb-4">Proudly Sponsored by LLW Consultancy Ltd</p>
                    <div class="d-grid gap-3 d-sm-flex justify-content-sm-center justify-content-xl-start">
                        <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-4 me-sm-3" href="#features">Get Started</a>
                        <a class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg px-4" href="<%= about_us_path %>">Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xl-5 col-xxl-6 text-center">
                <div id="productCarousel" class="carousel slide my-5 rounded-3" data-bs-ride="carousel">
                    <div class="carousel-inner rounded-3">
                        <div class="carousel-item active">
                            <%= image_tag "slides/london.jpeg", class: "d-block w-100 img-fluid", alt: "Slide 1" %>
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <%= image_tag "slides/statue.webp", class: "d-block w-100 img-fluid", alt: "Slide 2" %>
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <%= image_tag "slides/class91.jpg", class: "d-block w-100 img-fluid", alt: "Slide 3" %>
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <%= image_tag "slides/cc201830.jpg", class: "d-block w-100 img-fluid", alt: "Slide 3" %>
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <%= image_tag "slides/class88.png", class: "d-block w-100 img-fluid", alt: "Slide 4" %>
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <%= image_tag "gallery/2025convention/feature_bg.png", class: "d-block w-100 img-fluid", alt: "Slide 3" %>
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <%= image_tag "gallery/presidentworldwide2.jpg", class: "d-block w-100 img-fluid", alt: "Slide 4" %>
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <%= image_tag "slides/schoolgate.jpg", class: "d-block w-100 img-fluid", alt: "Slide 4" %>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#productCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
                        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
                    </button>
                    <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#productCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
                        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</header>
<!-- Features section-->
<section class="py-5" id="features">
    <div class="container px-5 my-5">
        <div class="row gx-5">
            <div class="col-lg-4 mb-5 mb-lg-0">
                <h2 class="fw-bolder mb-0">A Few Words About ICCOBA.</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <div class="row gx-5 row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2">
                    <div class="col mb-5 h-100">
                        <div class="feature bg-primary bg-gradient text-white rounded-3 mb-3"><i class="bi bi-book"></i></div>
                        <h2 class="h5">Honoring the Legacy</h2>
                        <p class="mb-0">The Immaculate Conception College Old Boys’ Association (ICCOBA) was first envisioned by Mr. Wilson Uwaifo in 1964. It began as a call to reconnect, support, and uplift the legacy of ICC Benin.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col mb-5 h-100">
                        <div class="feature bg-primary bg-gradient text-white rounded-3 mb-3"><i class="bi bi-award"></i></div>
                        <h2 class="h5">A History of Excellence</h2>
                        <p class="mb-0">With a proud heritage spanning over 78 years, ICC Benin has shaped generations of men who have gone on to make meaningful contributions across various sectors worldwide.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col mb-5 mb-md-0 h-100">
                        <div class="feature bg-primary bg-gradient text-white rounded-3 mb-3"><i class="bi bi-person-plus"></i></div>
                        <h2 class="h5">Who Can Join?</h2>
                        <p class="mb-0">Membership is open to all former students who spent at least three years at ICC Benin. Whether you're based in the UK or anywhere else, you're part of this family.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col h-100">
                        <div class="feature bg-primary bg-gradient text-white rounded-3 mb-3"><i class="bi bi-archive"></i></div>
                        <h2 class="h5">Why It Matters</h2>
                        <p class="mb-0">ICCOBA exists to build community, preserve the school's values, support current students, and give back meaningfully together.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<!-- Testimonial section-->
<div class="py-5 bg-light">
    <div class="container px-5 my-5">
        <div class="row gx-5 justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-10 col-xl-7">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <div class="fs-4 mb-4 fst-italic">"Being part of ICCOBA keeps me connected to my roots while making a real impact back home. Every project and event reminds me that together, we’re building more than memories, we’re shaping the future of ICC."</div>
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
                        <%= image_tag "gallery/presidentworldwide40.jpg", class: "rounded-circle me-3", alt: "..." %>
                        <div class="fw-bold">
                            President,
                            <span class="fw-bold text-primary mx-1">/</span>
                            ICCOBA Worldwide
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<!-- Blog preview section-->
<section class="py-5">
    <div class="container px-5 my-5">
        <div class="row gx-5 justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-8 col-xl-6">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <h2 class="fw-bolder">From our blog</h2>
                    <p class="lead fw-normal text-muted mb-5">Stay updated with the latest news, stories, and highlights from ICCOBAUK covering events, achievements, and community updates worldwide.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row gx-5">
            <div class="col-lg-4 mb-5">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow border-0">
                    <%= image_tag "gallery/pleaseregistersmall.jpg", class: "card-img-top", alt: "...600x350" %>
                    <div class="card-body p-4">
                        <div class="badge bg-primary bg-gradient rounded-pill mb-2">News</div>
                        <a class="text-decoration-none link-dark stretched-link" href="<%= blog_post_path %>">
                            <h5 class="card-title mb-3">Welcome to the ICCOBAUK/EUROPE ANNUAL CONVENTION 2025!</h5>
                        </a>
                        <p class="card-text mb-0">This highly anticipated event is happening soon at the DoubleTree by Hilton Coventry, promising an unforgettable in-person experience for all attendees.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer p-4 pt-0 bg-transparent border-top-0">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-end justify-content-between">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                <%= image_tag "gallery/small/llw-cssmall40.png", class: "rounded-circle me-3", alt: "..." %>
                                <div class=" small">
                                    <div class="fw-bold">Adewale Adesina</div>
                                    <div class="text-muted">September 05, 2025 &middot; 2 min read</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 mb-5">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow border-0">
                    <%= image_tag "gallery/presidentworldwide2.jpg", class: "card-img-top", alt: "...600x350" %>
                    <div class="card-body p-4">
                        <div class="badge bg-primary bg-gradient rounded-pill mb-2">News</div>
                        <a class="text-decoration-none link-dark stretched-link" href="<%= blog_post2_path %>">
                            <h5 class="card-title mb-3">ICCOBAUK/EUROPE ANNUAL CONVENTION 2025!</h5>
                        </a>
                        <p class="card-text mb-0">The ICCOBA Worldwide President has made a remarkable financial contribution in support of the upcoming 2025 Convention. His generosity highlights a strong commitment to the association’s vision and to strengthening the bond among Old Boys across the globe. The donation will go a long way in ensuring a successful and memorable gathering for all members.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer p-4 pt-0 bg-transparent border-top-0">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-end justify-content-between">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                <%= image_tag "gallery/small/cc20186small40.jpg", class: "rounded-circle me-3", alt: "..." %>
                                <div class=" small">
                                    <div class="fw-bold">Louis Ubebe</div>
                                    <div class="text-muted">September 01, 2025 &middot; 2 min read</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 mb-5">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow border-0">
                    <%= image_tag "gallery/llw-cs.png", class: "card-img-top", alt: "...600x350" %>
                    <div class="card-body p-4">
                        <div class="badge bg-primary bg-gradient rounded-pill mb-2">Latest News</div>
                        <a class="text-decoration-none link-dark stretched-link" href="<%= blog_post3_path %>">
                            <h5 class="card-title mb-3">LLW Consultancy: London’s Rising Tech Power</h5>
                        </a>
                        <p class="card-text mb-0">LLW Consultancy Services is rapidly emerging as a tech giant in London, UK, dedicated to delivering innovative solutions for businesses across industries. Our team of skilled developers, cloud engineers, and IT strategists are committed to transforming ideas into scalable, efficient technology products that meet the demands of the modern market.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer p-4 pt-0 bg-transparent border-top-0">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-end justify-content-between">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                <%= image_tag "gallery/small/cc20186small40.jpg", class: "rounded-circle me-3", alt: "..." %>
                                <div class=" small">
                                    <div class="fw-bold">Louis Ubebe</div>
                                    <div class="text-muted">August 18, 2025 &middot; 4 min read</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Call to action-->
            <aside class="bg-primary bg-gradient rounded-3 p-4 p-sm-5 mt-5">
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between flex-column flex-xl-row text-center text-xl-start">
                    <div class="mb-4 mb-xl-0">
                        <div class="fs-3 fw-bold text-white">New products, delivered to you.</div>
                        <div class="text-white-50">Sign up for our newsletter for the latest updates.</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ms-xl-4">
                        <div class="input-group mb-2">
                            <input class="form-control" type="text" placeholder="Email address..." aria-label="Email address..." aria-describedby="button-newsletter" />
                            <button class="btn btn-outline-light" id="button-newsletter" type="button">Sign up</button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="small text-white-50">We care about privacy, and will never share your data.</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </aside>
        </div>
</section>
</main>
